", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982645_1000853181732648_5055517427829171192_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=FBQp0223NlYQ7kNvgG83cJ7&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBVMX1X482XDx7P-aE4iW407xViAdSd8OjaE2SMq2bD1Q&oe=6730B717"}, {"file_name": "port.png", "id": "820373836744300", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75203626_820373840077633_3034343047413447332_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=6_-yZaE1pHwQ7kNvgFgJQfs&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD7gNgH4x5qF-oiI0ddQc2-JWEBu8N326gU1kCN33cFQQ&oe=6730A8DD"}, {"file_name": "ml.png", "id": "502579852256353", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036644_502579858923019_3842705229132857953_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=1rpoN7hbPbgQ7kNvgEoqYTh&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDeVQg4rNtHgva9KSgoo4LqDeg0eUiZhzx3YdltYieGTw&oe=67309186"}, {"file_name": "landscape.png", "id": "465213706424419", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003266_465213709757752_680111565771229398_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=K1A_TeuY2fYQ7kNvgFWLe34&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAeQ7LEzC1rC92pRAO8Zo_-awRhVbE56anhIphXfV5xnw&oe=6730ADAE"}]}, "id": "695307962768721", "locale": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "4.png", "id": "964615488773393", "uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982581_964615495440059_2784752763184915334_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=jYK0UbsRSA0Q7kNvgH8Lklt&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCktZvjFH2CVbynxGHgK9xIgvmVATKIk-OXt_3aC12Z9w&oe=6730AB6A"}, {"file_name": "2.png", "id": "1943374952743027", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974836_1943374956076360_2484593514118294358_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=xCDctMHMI9gQ7kNvgGLvNuv&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCnnS1pg2WzepUKIO7KQLlF9Stgz4_pdzWEz6S2lXNe1Q&oe=6730A902"}, {"file_name": "1.png", "id": "445060168517426", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75462964_445060171850759_5520915542327767111_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=M07m_o_o-TsQ7kNvgFZHRid&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBXBoNXEI_vWqVAxoJK4QfpyWfpAmCqUiMdNgpy5aWtXA&oe=67309584"}, {"file_name": "5.png", "id": "467916352871409", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003282_467916356204742_1871921057092171900_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=lxmiBgz0OwkQ7kNvgEsaSHl&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCQ8U15seKvnlgL31PmP2_UX7QXYcXfmSiy6KIrMAXVYw&oe=6730B262"}, {"file_name": "3.png", "id": "1934382610375855", "uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974473_1934382613709188_7156337812617042679_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Rn7RscjgRqQQ7kNvgFjA6Xo&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCpu9dkJpXN24EtF93HAd_i_sPmxMfYDnDiUvZ12rChMA&oe=67309C73"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "landscape.png", "id": "1524760081483769", "uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974531_1524760084817102_6497712644828891067_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=4I3XtqjomcEQ7kNvgFA-ijJ&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA83A-WRgh-9uAe_dE4Hy7Wg3c7BII84Dlyd4QURsHO_Q&oe=67309B6F"}, "display_name": "Mystery Box VR: Hidden Secrets", "keywords": [], "long_description": " AN IMMERSIVE VR PUZZLE EXPERIENCE\nInteract with objects, handles, buttons, and wheels on each side. Crack enigmas and collect hidden puzzle tiles on a random side of the boxes.\n\nYou won't be able to compare reality with fiction.\n\n# DISCOVER INVENTIONS\nOnce you unlock all 8 boxes of a Level Pack, you can compose a puzzle and discover a brief history of an invention.\n\nIt's not always easy to escape the room, so use all your IQ to crack the riddles. There's a logic behind all of them, even where it seems it's not!\n\n# IMMERSIVE SOUNDTRACK\nPlay the game with your headphones to get immersed in this amazing adventure.\n\n# HINTS\nGot stuck on some enigma? No worries, you can still get a helpful hint! You can also get in touch with me in case you really can't make it through a riddle, I'll be glad to help ;)\n\n# MULTILANGUAGE\nAvailable in English, French, Italian, German, Spanish, Russian, and Japanese.\n\nThe game language will change automatically based on the language settings of your device", "short_description": "A VR escape room game where you have to solve intriguing riddles to open boxes and discover nice stories about popular inventions!"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "$R36BSY5.png", "id": "3678762505771822", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031430_3678762509105155_2151975047074617165_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=hHSx5fUHjbcQ7kNvgG7FhSz&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD8prRpo0kpBZwCwOgsgXSyHwsVucTEcobbqj4FNfA4Fg&oe=67309765"}, {"file_name": "$R81V725.png", "id": "2720695481426567", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75262743_2720695484759900_604086922326600035_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=KMWtDYK4e9UQ7kNvgGqpY3X&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCXDjaddVQ_HriY_WFnhkoBXuB8d8Z2HMV0N6Rdoxr77A&oe=6730964D"}, {"file_name": "$RQ3SN6U.png", "id": "1552311425628973", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982519_1552311428962306_1218130395049083834_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=6CdTcNkkYx8Q7kNvgHcyV8W&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=